{"tid":250461,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[公屋撚］點樣舉報隔離屋養狗","createTime":"2017-05-20T05:51:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-12T00:45:12.000Z","uid":13739,"like":34,"dislike":165,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"93afa93d723729e2441927ef806f92f5507fc766","tid":250461,"uid":13739,"like":0,"dislike":17,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T05:51:58.000Z","msg":"上星期開始，隔離屋晚晚都有狗吠聲叫到十一二點，但我知佢地一向都冇養狗。有一日同𨋢見到面，八卦問下，原來佢地有親戚屋企裝修，暫時住酒店3個月，隻狗要暫住佢地屋企3個月，但佢未養過狗，話隻狗嘈親我地好唔好意思。<br />\n<br />\n問題係，我準備緊cfa考試真係好需要安靜環境溫書，另外，我媽係好憎狗既人，聽到狗叫聲會好燥，之後成日燥我底。<br />\n<br />\n想問大家，舉報房署完係咪好快做野？<br />\n<br />\n利申：隔離屋只有兩母女，幾年同佢老公離婚，之後分戶。阿媽係目測35以上，b-c cup，識打扮，見過佢冇戴bra倒垃圾。個女剛上大學，有宿舍住，但周六日都會返屋企，幾高下160左右，冇咩波，cute cute 樣。"},{"pid":"644015f08c874f8151f6f3dbfea5c4921a247a8b","tid":250461,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T05:53:25.000Z","msg":"打1823"},{"pid":"a7b80b5cfec833512cb17c359c6234d3a9c1b8ed","tid":250461,"uid":27770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T05:54:57.000Z","msg":"唔好恰人地兩母女啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0a68b809e77920c6e71735d0d04a547b12fedb4","tid":250461,"uid":81277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T05:55:26.000Z","msg":"娛樂台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b8ec442b8c91d68a44d3733c5591488784a7892","tid":250461,"uid":40624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T05:55:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最撚憎人養狗"},{"pid":"339e4968dd6ee02dcad0ef1caa3b1fc6b2ea3495","tid":250461,"uid":59114,"like":48,"dislike":1,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T05:56:36.000Z","msg":"點解要講埋兩母女身材<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連登好撚恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b2af70e95f6b