"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/20/143805_a23cc9e23a4aafc9be35b872adb4a80a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F20%2F143805_a23cc9e23a4aafc9be35b872adb4a80a.jpg&h=8d3bef02&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/20/143806_0a07e674b653ab30282eb4e65c74e2e0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F20%2F143806_0a07e674b653ab30282eb4e65c74e2e0.jpg&h=8a2134e1&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5067c316b6ffc00d54c611d6fb17e074742eb244","tid":250461,"uid":19923,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T07:21:49.000Z","msg":"等睇樓主趕走人隻狗都照fail，然後搵唔到藉口賴地硬個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bee2846b12ae121acec15ef640bf99adfeb8588d","tid":250461,"uid":64044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T07:36:50.000Z","msg":"收皮啦你"},{"pid":"145e00a9f83a021985324c92ece5754d137e9ae3","tid":250461,"uid":11256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T07:44:47.000Z","msg":"其實人地有得揀會放公屋咩？<br />\n貪公屋香呀？<br />\n窮人真係特別煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再講 狗仔開頭唔慣 <br />\n公屋隔音差過私樓好多<br />\n過幾日習慣左人地開門聲就無事<br />\n狗都住私樓呀 你呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你投訴完又點 會有私樓住咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df30530d13cace4137b11c395f6d1b85bb306cac","tid":250461,"uid":11973,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T07:45:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係兩三個月就隻眼開隻眼閉算啦</blockquote><br />\n一個月唔夠就考試啦...成萬蚊考一次，靠今個study leave搏盡佢</blockquote><br />\n唔關狗事ga<br />\n人蠢就點都肥</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪係<br />\n吠幾聲就分心<br />\n咁你返工啲同事傾偈大聲啲都分心㗎啦<br />\n咁唔撚駛做嘢啦<br />\n<br />\n你話人哋長期偷養長期滋擾都話呀<br />\n咁巴閉要寧靜環境咪住私樓囉<br />\n再唔係咪出去租幾個月service apartment 囉<br />\n又冇錢喎<br />\n又想搞鳩人喎<br />\n<br />\n睇你要考得呢啲試都係打工㗎啦<br />\n就算俾你考到你老細咪又係當你狗咁撚<br />\n咁人哋又投訴你呀?"},{"pid":"4851e9870a57eedbd21f29ec303a221325321d74","tid":250461,"uid":57914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T07:45:22.000Z","msg":"房署，1823揾，要求電話答覆跟進情況<br />\n致電保安/物業管理公司<br />\n報警等差人上佢門跟進"},{"pid":"78dfda4b4fae0e3952fcaef8fb05d4262ae93e15","tid":250461,"uid":62646,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T07:48:45.000Z","msg":"公屋根本唔應該養動物<br />\n咁撚多on9鬧樓主既<br />\n我支持你舉報<br />\n最好將住公屋揸靚車個d一次過報哂上去叫佢查<br />\n浪費資源"},{"pid":"bbecef3b06e16a66763a5342e2b675d7d9589b4e","tid":250461,"uid":28464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T07:48:45.000Z","msg":"咪撚on9 賴隻狗"},{"pid":"be1ebcc38ea7be08dc5ce89c321367ae97c62455","tid":250461,"uid":46842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T07:50:08.000Z","msg":"如果係麻甩佬應該過萬正皮"},{"pid":"bc57b00d2aef1d2c7832543fc8b1dfdabd53c7d8","tid":250461,"uid":39729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T07:56:38.000Z","msg":"溫書啦，仲上連登？"},{"pid":"f7865e44dbd27b84b5bc0a2a4a9c1ef356d77620","tid":250461,"uid":11774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T07:58:43.000Z","msg":"唔識去自修室<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9dbb2debbd3b333915d43c8c612fd06db8ca472","tid":250461,"uid":15921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T08:01:00.000Z","msg":"要靜就去拉把啦<br />\n你玩野佢裝修你仲仆街"},{"pid":"f0d54dd3fb4528ed8cb26638ec7dcde221be858d","tid":250461,"uid":19408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T08:04:40.000Z","msg":"樓主狗都不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1e301b8860b4e994ebe66135efce0349403e001","tid":250461,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T08:05:40.000Z","msg":"你住邊？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 舉報埋你個仆街呀 屌你老母"},{"pid":"41ba38c86ea746189a3857e8af2fee7ba7ab3d79","tid":250461,"uid":42722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T08:07:44.000Z","msg":"樓主 你正一垃撚圾， 人地隻狗都係住三個月， 你自己廢就咪撚瀨隻狗啦，你投訴完  隻狗無地地方住， 你間接害撚死隻狗啊， 垃圾 你狗都不如，你唔識去自修室既？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f369a43e6d2d0c4bd55b47d9c9f7593f4db177f4","tid":250461,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T08:09:34.000Z","msg":"咁都專心唔到 渣ga"},{"pid":"f9589fa47a872541602b55e7f38b82bb044f4ff8","tid":250461,"uid":29880,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T08:18:34.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n我同啊媽一齊住緊公屋<br />\n近排有個親戚要裝修<br />\n拜托我地湊住隻狗先<br />\n但係隻狗一到11,12點就係咁吠<br />\n嘈到隔離屋個毒撚<br />\n我話隻狗擺住喺到3個月<br />\n叫佢體諒下<br />\n近排我發現佢成日偷望我老母倒垃圾<br />\n又成日色迷迷咁望住我<br />\n唔知佢係咪想話隻狗嘈親佢要肉償<br />\n宜家好驚,報唔報警好?"},{"pid":"80035b88be52dc6e9ce073295dfa07c14a4702ab","tid":250461,"uid":42009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T08:19:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解要講埋兩母女身材<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連登好撚恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc26b50c466ab5523046a4ecb93b60d7ecd648b5","tid":250461,"uid":29299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T08:21:02.000Z","msg":"考唔掂搵藉口俾自己<br />\n死廢柴"},{"pid":"f08e03741823f1daff1e1b15ee20fb93eb32c72d","tid":250461,"uid":29299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T08:25:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>考唔掂搵藉口俾自己<br />\n死廢柴</blockquote><br />\n係搵定藉口<br />\n係現實入面一定係條廢柴<br />\n利申：我認我都係咁,但唔會搞鳩人"},{"pid":"b01fca96d6d092ac346bfe9f3a7b9519827766b7","tid":250461,"uid":62646,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T08:25:47.000Z","msg":"如果係死廢老養狗我肯定呢個post的反應係調轉<br />\n連登有女為大 厹到一個點"},{"pid":"0404e3de33c4f13f8a8f00cad422a5e9fd5d78e3","tid":250461,"uid":62650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T08:29:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>考唔掂搵藉口俾自己<br />\n死廢柴</blockquote><br />\n係搵定藉口<br />\n係現實入面一定係條廢柴<br />\n利申：我認我都係咁,但唔會搞鳩人</blockquote><br />\n我成日搵籍口唔溫書...呢D 係其中一個例子"},{"pid":"a19905b737a410d0b1a50ec92c5957cf9895c610","tid":250461,"uid":60219,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T08:35:36.000Z","msg":"呢個post既留言真係癡線，竟然個個係到blame the victim<br />\n個親戚放隻狗去寵物酒店咪得囉<br />\n明明係個親戚又寒酸又自私為咗慳自己錢就要嘈到人地鄰居<br />\n不過我唔建議樓主直接搵房署<br />\n不妨先同個鄰居攤牌話你就快考試所以唔想被嘈到，要求佢送隻狗去寵物酒店先<br />\n如果佢唔肯接受即係佢係自私精，你可以大條道理去房署投訴"}]}